name: CC_acwo
notes: Pure water offsets for the absorption channels from ACS device (calibration) file [m-1].

name: CC_awlngth
notes: Wavelengths at which the absorption measurements were made [nm].

name: CC_ccwo
notes: Pure water offsets for the beam attenuation channels from ACS device (calibration) file [m-1].

name: CC_cwlngth
notes: Attenuation channel wavelengths [nm], from ACS device (calibration) file.

name: CC_taarray
notes: Instrument, wavelength, and channel ('a') specific internal temperature calibration correction coefficients from ACS device (calibration) file [m-1].

name: CC_tbins
notes: Instrument specific internal temperature calibration bin values from ACS device (calibration) file [deg_C].

name: CC_tcal
notes: Factory calibration reference (pure water) temperature [deg_C] supplied by the instrument manufacturer (WETLabs).

name: CC_tcarray
notes: Instrument, wavelength, and channel ('c') specific internal temperature calibration correction coefficients from ACS device (calibration) file [m-1].
